<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Resources on Jikkou</title><link>https://www.jikkou.io/docs/providers/apacheiceberg/resources/</link><description>Recent content in Resources on Jikkou</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://www.jikkou.io/docs/providers/apacheiceberg/resources/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Iceberg Namespace</title><link>https://www.jikkou.io/docs/providers/apacheiceberg/resources/iceberg-namespace/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.jikkou.io/docs/providers/apacheiceberg/resources/iceberg-namespace/</guid><description>&lt;div class="pageinfo pageinfo-info">
&lt;p>&lt;code>IcebergNamespace&lt;/code> resources are used to define the namespaces (databases) you want to manage in your
Iceberg catalog. A namespace groups tables and carries metadata as key/value properties.&lt;/p>

&lt;/div>

&lt;h2 id="icebergnamespace">&lt;code>IcebergNamespace&lt;/code>&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="specification">Specification&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>Here is the &lt;em>resource definition file&lt;/em> for defining an &lt;code>IcebergNamespace&lt;/code>.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">apiVersion&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;iceberg.jikkou.io/v1beta1&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># The api version (required)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">kind&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;IcebergNamespace&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># The resource kind (required)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;namespace name&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Dot-separated namespace path (required)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">labels&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>{&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>}&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">annotations&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>{&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>}&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">properties&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Namespace-level metadata (optional)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">&amp;lt;key&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;value&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>The &lt;code>metadata.name&lt;/code> property is mandatory. Nested namespaces are expressed using dot notation —
for example, &lt;code>analytics.events&lt;/code> creates a namespace &lt;code>events&lt;/code> inside &lt;code>analytics&lt;/code>.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Iceberg Table</title><link>https://www.jikkou.io/docs/providers/apacheiceberg/resources/iceberg-table/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.jikkou.io/docs/providers/apacheiceberg/resources/iceberg-table/</guid><description>&lt;div class="pageinfo pageinfo-info">
&lt;p>&lt;code>IcebergTable&lt;/code> resources are used to define the tables you want to manage in your Iceberg catalog.
An &lt;code>IcebergTable&lt;/code> resource defines the schema, partition layout, sort order, and table-level
properties. Jikkou performs safe schema evolution — adding, renaming, updating, and dropping
columns — without data loss.&lt;/p>

&lt;/div>

&lt;h2 id="icebergtable">&lt;code>IcebergTable&lt;/code>&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="specification">Specification&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>Here is the &lt;em>resource definition file&lt;/em> for defining an &lt;code>IcebergTable&lt;/code>.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">apiVersion&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;iceberg.jikkou.io/v1beta1&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># The api version (required)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">kind&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;IcebergTable&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># The resource kind (required)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;namespace&amp;gt;.&amp;lt;table&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Fully qualified table name (required)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">labels&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>{&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>}&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">annotations&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>{&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>}&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">location&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;storage path&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Override the default table location (optional)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">schema&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">identifierFields&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Primary-key columns for MERGE/UPSERT semantics (optional)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;column name&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">columns&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Ordered list of columns (required)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;column name&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Column name (required)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;type&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Column type (required) — see type reference below&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">required: &amp;lt;true|false&amp;gt; # Whether the column is non-nullable (default&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="kc">false&lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">doc&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;description&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Documentation string (optional)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">default&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;value&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Initial default value, immutable after creation (optional)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">writeDefault&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;value&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Write-default for absent values, updatable (optional)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">previousName&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;old name&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Triggers a safe rename instead of drop+add (optional)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">partitionFields&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Partition layout (optional)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">sourceColumn&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;column&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Source column to partition on (required)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">transform&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;transform&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Partition transform (required) — see transforms below&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;partition field name&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Custom partition field name (optional)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">sortFields&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Default write sort order (optional)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">column&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;column&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Column name (mutually exclusive with term)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">term&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;expression&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Sort expression e.g. bucket[16](user_id) (mutually exclusive with column)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">direction: &amp;lt;asc|desc&amp;gt; # Sort direction (default&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">asc)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">nullOrder: &amp;lt;first|last&amp;gt; # Null placement (default&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">last)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">properties&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Table-level metadata properties (optional)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">&amp;lt;key&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;value&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="column-types">Column Types&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>Jikkou maps a set of type strings to the underlying Iceberg types:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Iceberg View</title><link>https://www.jikkou.io/docs/providers/apacheiceberg/resources/iceberg-view/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.jikkou.io/docs/providers/apacheiceberg/resources/iceberg-view/</guid><description>&lt;div class="pageinfo pageinfo-info">
&lt;p>&lt;code>IcebergView&lt;/code> resources are used to define SQL views in your Iceberg catalog.
A view is a logical definition backed by one or more SQL queries — the output schema
is inferred by the engine and populated on collect.&lt;/p>

&lt;/div>

&lt;h2 id="icebergview">&lt;code>IcebergView&lt;/code>&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="specification">Specification&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>Here is the &lt;em>resource definition file&lt;/em> for defining an &lt;code>IcebergView&lt;/code>.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">apiVersion&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;iceberg.jikkou.io/v1beta1&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># The api version (required)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">kind&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;IcebergView&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># The resource kind (required)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;namespace&amp;gt;.&amp;lt;view&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Fully qualified view name (required)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">labels&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>{&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>}&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">annotations&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>{&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>}&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">schema&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Output schema (read-only, inferred by the engine)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">columns&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;column name&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;type&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">required&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;true|false&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">doc&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;description&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">queries&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># SQL query definitions (at least one required)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">sql&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;SQL SELECT statement&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># The SQL defining the view (required)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">dialect&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;dialect&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># SQL dialect e.g. &amp;#39;spark&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;trino&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;presto&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;hive&amp;#39; (required)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">defaultNamespace&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">&amp;lt;namespace&amp;gt; &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># Default namespace for unqualified table references (optional)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
